<para style="p">A psalm of David. A maschil.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Blessed is the person whose transgression is forgiven,</para>

<para style="q1">whose sin is covered.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Blessed is the man to whom Yahweh reckons no guilt</para>

<para style="q1">and in whose spirit there is no deceit.</para>
